{
  "texts": [
    "All instructions are generated by the model.",
    "The entire dataset is currently open source.",
    "• BELLE train 1M CN (BELLEGroup, 2023).",
    "The BELLE train 1M CN dataset is part of the Chinese training data for the BELLE model, comprising around 917K Chinese instructions.",
    "It shares the same construction method as the BELLE train 0.5M CN, but it undergoes post-processing to remove low-quality data."
  ]
}